node_6.description: This is Rajiv Patel's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 9:00 am, have a light breakfast at 9:30 am, work on his paintings at the artist co-living space from 10:00 am to 1:00 pm, take a break for lunch at 1:00 pm, continue painting from 2:00 pm to 5:00 pm, attend a guitar lesson at 6:00 pm, have dinner at 7:00 pm, relax and unwind by playing the guitar or watching TV from 8:00 pm onwards.
